data.value: This is adjustable custom logo. Based on custom logos (which means lower resolution for you), this allows you to create your own color variation of World of Warcraft logo. You cannot set background color with these.

data.name: label25.Text
data.value:
Axxa's Wow Logo Creator v1.2 ====================
Wow Logo Creator is simple tool, that lets you create your own wow-lik logos. If you would be interested in source code, i have released versions 1.0 code, you can download it at >>>> http://filebeam.com/19e37dace464d04d562c19b781345716 . Images (mainly main text letters) comes from old logo generator. Most of shield images comes from Blizzard, many of them have been edited by me. Blue shield 2 and RD shield is from devianart (low resolution ftw).
====Whats new in v1.2==== - New functionality: user adjustable shield - Redone interface - New shields - Enhanced text rendering
====Whats new in v1.1==== - Redone interface - Added possibility to force size of subtext - Added many positioning features; - You can manualy set vertical and horizontal position of main text - You can manualy set vertical and horizontal position of subtext
Coded in C# by Axxa, for wowresource.eu. Feel free to share this program with your friends, on your website and such. Please note that this version should be considered as pretty much close to final.
